filter, which is at the

01:06:21.140 --> 01:06:25.390
receiver, which is q of t and
you want the product of t and

01:06:25.390 --> 01:06:28.290
you want the convolution of all
of those to satisfy the

01:06:28.290 --> 01:06:30.110
