01:06:43.010 --> 01:06:46.480
The channel filter up at pass
band, we've seen that one of

01:06:46.480 --> 01:06:49.350
the things that it can be viewed
as doing is putting

01:06:49.350 --> 01:06:53.200
Doppler shift into this input.

01:06:53.200 --> 01:06:58.600
So what comes in at some
frequency f is now going to be

01:06:58.600 --> 01:07:02.710
coming through here at some
slightly different frequency.

01:07:02.710 --> 01:07:05.730
We then add white noise to it.

01:07:05.730 --> 01:07:09.790
We then get y of t out, which
has now been shifted around

01:07:09.790 --> 01:07:12.520
