a little bit.

01:07:12.520 --> 01:07:15.100
We go through a frequency
demodulation.

01:07:15.100 --> 01:07:18.390
We get down frequency
to modulation by

01:07:18.390 --> 01:07:20.450
this carrier frequency.

01:07:20.450 --> 01:07:28.420
We get down to v of t, which
is now a baseband complex

01:07:28.420 --> 01:07:31.770
