at baseband and also looking

01:07:54.510 --> 01:07:58.470
at filters at pass band, we
would like to be able to take

01:07:58.470 --> 01:08:02.680
some baseband equivalent
of this filter here.

01:08:02.680 --> 01:08:04.780
So what we're going to do
is look at the baseband

01:08:04.780 --> 01:08:06.080
equivalent.

01:08:09.050 --> 01:08:12.930
The system function at baseband
corresponding to this

01:08:12.930 --> 01:08:17.760
